---
description: Delegation-first delivery discipline
alwaysApply: true
---

For any non-trivial task, behave as an orchestrator first:

1) make a short plan
2) call matching specialist subagents before implementation
3) summarize specialist findings
4) implement only after specialist input
5) run verification checks before commit recommendation

Before final response, add a "Delegation report" that includes:
- delegated specialists and why they were selected
- key recommendations from each specialist
- whether delegation improved outcome (success/partial/failure)
- checks executed (lint, typecheck, tests, build, security if relevant)
- residual risk

If no delegation was used, provide a concrete reason and explicit risk statement.
